=Richard E. Strassberg (1948-)=
Professor of Chinese at the University of California  Los Angeles
==Publications== 
===PhD Disseration===
* The Peach Blossom Fan: Personal Cultivation in a Chinese Drama. Princeton University, 1975
===Monographs===
* Inscribed landscapes: travel writing from imperial China. University of Californnia Press, 1994
* A Chinese Bestiary: Strange Creatures from the Guideways through Mountains and Seas. University of Californnia Press, 2002
* Wandering Spirits: Chen Shiyuan's Encyclopedia of Dreams. University of Californnia Press, 2008